Package: oecdr
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the OECD SDMX REST API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hyungbae", "Cho", email = "bwade9090@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Utilities for fetching OECD statistics from the SDMX REST API
    (<https://sdmx.oecd.org>), converting responses to tibbles, and persisting
    them to relational databases via the 'DBI' interface. Supports SQLite by
    default, with optional PostgreSQL support.
URL: https://github.com/bwade9090/oecdr
BugReports: https://github.com/bwade9090/oecdr/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    tibble,
    DBI,
    RSQLite,
    readr,
    utils
